  "content": "# Comprehensive Audit Findings — 2026-03-19\n\n## Code Quality (98 clippy warnings)\n- 37 deprecated bollard API calls in docker.rs (needs dependency upgrade)\n- 40 collapsible if statements in corvia-kernel (autofix-eligible)\n- 11 large Err-variant warnings in corvia-inference\n- 57 production unwrap() calls (24 in mcp.rs, 13 RwLock in clustering.rs)\n- 18+ magic strings (\"user-history\", \"claude-sessions\", \"corvia\") need constants\n\n## Bugs Fixed\n- Session endpoints returned 500 instead of 404 for missing sessions (heartbeat, commit, rollback)\n- Silent `let _ =` on store.insert() in merge_worker and commit_pipeline — now logs warnings\n- Dashboard traces page showed all zeros — fixed with DashboardTraceLayer\n\n## Hooks Audit\n- Static Claude Code hooks + generated corvia hooks coexist in .claude/settings.json\n- Doc-placement hook and git hooks not auto-invoked in devcontainer (manual init-hooks needed)\n- Agent registration hook is display-only, doesn't actually register\n\n## API Testing (49 endpoints, 38 PASS, 3 FAIL fixed)\n- gc/history and gc/stats endpoints return 404 (routes not registered in running binary)\n- /v1/ask and /api/dashboard/rag/ask can timeout and crash server (needs request timeout)\n- ingest/sessions returns 500 (adapter binary not on PATH)",
